PrecisAuthority for the Minister (a) to sign a Convention with the REPUBLIC OF SOUTH AFRICA for the AVOIDANCE OF DOUBLE TAXATION and the PREVENTION OF FISCAL EVASION with respect to TAXES ON INCOME, or (b) to issue an Instrument of Full Powers authorizing the Hon.
